{White's heavy forces are directed toward the g7 square. Time is ripe for a stunning blow.} 1. Nd5 $1 {Clearance!} exd5 2. Qxg7+ $3 {A master shot! White sacrifices the queen, but thanks to a beautiful windmill tactic will recover material with interest.} (2. Bxg7 $2 {Looks decisive enough. However, Black has the strong deflection} Bh3 $1 3. Qxh3 Nxg7 {when he ends up with an extra piece.}) 2... Nxg7 3. Rxg7+ Kh8 4. Rxe7+ {The point of White's previous play. Next we capture the queen.} 1-0

