White's bishop. Bd3 is our idea, setting up a killer battery. Black should bail out with} 13... cxd4 {but then the endgame after} 14. Qxd4 {is better for White. White has the better knight, better bishop, better rooks and better king! Once again we would like to refer you to the Spielmann - Grau [/variation/25618985] model game, which is very instructive.}) *

